01:07:32.590 --> 01:07:40.639
♪ It is the night of the dearsaviour's birth. ♪

01:07:40.639 --> 01:07:47.938
♪ Long lay the world insin and error pining, ♪

01:07:47.938 --> 01:07:49.607
♪ 'til he appeared

01:07:49.648 --> 01:07:55.446
♪ and the soul feltits worth. ♪

01:07:55.488 --> 01:08:01.702
♪ A thrill of hope the wearysoul rejoices, ♪

01:08:01.744 --> 01:08:08.793
♪ for yonder breaks a newand glorious morn. ♪

01:08:08.793 --> 01:08:15.341
♪ Fall on your knees,

01:08:15.382 --> 01:08:21.846
♪ oh hear the angel voices.

01:08:21.889 --> 01:08:28.229
♪ Oh night divine,

01:08:28.270 --> 01:08:34.527
♪ oh night whenChrist was born. ♪

01:08:34.568 --> 01:08:41.908
♪ Oh night divine.

01:08:41.951 --> 01:08:45.078
♪ Oh night,

01:08:45.121 --> 01:08:51.877
♪ oh night divine.

01:08:51.877 --> 01:08:54.004
( applause )

01:08:54.004 --> 01:08:56.590
Thank you, thank you.

01:08:56.590 --> 01:08:59.593
And you on the piano,that was fabulous.

01:08:59.635 --> 01:09:02.805
So, are you single?

